<BaseLayout
  title="Contact BOSS Consult - Tech Recruitment Cape Town"
  description="Get in touch with BOSS Consult in Cape Town. Phone: +27 63 240 4447, Email: gaylene@bossenterprise.co.za. Submit your CV or enquire about our recruitment services."
>
  <main class="pt-24">
  <section class="bg-brand-dark text-white py-20"> <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center"> <h1>Get in Touch</h1> <p class="text-xl mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-brand-gray-lighter">
Have a question, or want to discuss your recruitment needs? We'd love to hear from you.
</p> </div> </section> <section class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-24"> <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"> <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16"> <div> <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-family-heading)] text-brand-dark mb-8">Send Us a Message</h2> <form action="https://api.web3forms.com/submit" method="POST" class="space-y-6">
